        "title": "Professional Summary",
        "data": {},
        "html": "<p>Results-driven <strong>Data Scientist</strong> with a Ph.D. in Statistics and 6+ years of experience transforming complex data into actionable business insights. Expertise in machine learning, deep learning, and statistical modeling with a focus on NLP and computer vision applications. Published researcher with 12+ peer-reviewed papers and a track record of deploying ML models that generated $20M+ in annual revenue impact.</p>"
